FRIJointOverlay

public FRIJointOverlay(FRISession friSession)
Create a new FRIJointOverlay to overlay joint specific motions. The default client command mode is ClientCommandMode#JOINT_POSITION.

Parameters:
friSession - the FRISession to use for the joint overlay.

FRIJointOverlay

public FRIJointOverlay(FRISession friSession,
                       ClientCommandMode commandMode)
Create a new FRIJointOverlay to overlay joint specific motions.

The parameter commandMode specifies, which command values are expected from the FRIClient for this overlay.

Parameters:
friSession - the FRISession to use for the joint overlay.
commandMode - the command mode of the FRI client.
Method Detail

overrideJointAcceleration

public void overrideJointAcceleration(double accelerationOverride)
Override the maximum allowed joint acceleration.

The value of accelerationOverride will be multiplied with the maximum allowed acceleration jerk.

Parameters:
accelerationOverride - override factor for acceleration (value between 1.0 and 20.0)
